OL,5, The strategy to tackle fraud and other 
OL,6, economic crime should be overhauled to 
OL,7, prevent scammers acting with           
OL,8, "impunity", according to MPs.          
OL,10,FMinisters should consider creating a   
OL,11,Fnew government department and a new law
OL,12,Fenforcement agency to get to grips with
OL,13,Fthe issue, the Treasury Committee said.
OL,15,FThe committee called for mandatory     
OL,16,Frefunds in push-payment fraud cases.   
OL,18,FThis is when victims transfer money to 
OL,19,Ffraudsters, thinking they are from     
OL,20,Fofficial organisations.                
